text.currentLevelDescription:
A target enemy unit within {[range]} receives a <style="Debuff_Markerlight">Markerlight</style> until the end of <style="Faction_Tau">Sho'syl</style>'s next turn.
At the beginning of <style="Faction_Tau">Sho'syl</style>'s next turn, if he is still in play, the target is hit by a Seeker Missile dealing <style="Stat_Hits">{[nrOfHits]}x</style> <style="DMG_Heavy">{[minDmg]}-{[maxDmg]} Heavy Round Damage</style>.

{[S/AbilityDamageExplanation]}

Marks a target hex and the two hexes behind it for 1 round. Deals <style="Stat_Hits">{[nrOfHits]}x</style> <style="DMG_Plasma">{[minDmg]}-{[maxDmg]} Plasma Damage</style> to all enemies in the marked area the first time an enemy unit ends their movement in it.

Initial <style="Cooldown">cooldown: {[initialCooldownTurns]} round</style>. 

{[S/AbilityDamageExplanation]}

Targets an enemy unit that has their <style="Stat_Armor">Armour</style> reduced or is within a friendly <style="ContagionsOfNurgle">Contagion</style> aura. Deals <style="Stat_Hits">{[nrOfHits]}x</style> <style="DMG_Energy">{[minDmg]}-{[maxDmg]} Energy Damage</style> to the target.

Cost: <style="Resource_MachinesOfWarAmmo">{[munitionsCost]} munition</style>.

{[S/AbilityDamageExplanation]}

Targets a hex on the battlefield. All enemies on that hex or adjacent hexes that also either have their <style="Stat_Armor">Armour</style> reduced or are within a friendly <style="ContagionsOfNurgle">Contagion</style> aura take <style="Stat_Hits">{[nrOfHits]}x</style> <style="DMG_Toxic">{[minDmg]}-{[maxDmg]} Toxic Damage</style> and become <style="Debuff_Pinned">Suppressed</style> for 1 round. Then adds <style="Tile_Contamination">Contamination</style> to the target hex and random hexes adjacent to it, up to a total of <style="Stat">{[nrOfTiles]}</style> hexes.

Initial <style="Cooldown">cooldown: {[initialCooldownTurns]} round</style>. 

{[S/AbilityDamageExplanation]}

Marks a hex on the battlefield and 3 additional hexes adjacent to it but not to each other. At the beginning of its next turn, deals <style="Stat_Hits">{[nrOfHits]}x</style> <style="DMG_Blast">{[minDmg]}-{[maxDmg]} Blast Damage</style> to all enemies on marked hexes. Each enemy unit hit has a <style="STAT">{[chance]}%</style> chance to increase the <style="Stat_Chance">Crit Chance</style> and <style="Stat_CritDamage">Crit Damage</style> of friendly units with <style="Act_Of_Faith">Act of Faith</style> as if a friendly <style="Aliance_Imperial">Imperial</style> unit had killed an enemy unit.

Initial <style="Cooldown">cooldown: {[initialCooldownTurns]} round</style>. 

{[S/AbilityDamageExplanation]}

Marks a free hex on the battlefield and additionally <style="Stat">{[nrOfTiles]}</style> random free hexes within range {[range]} of the target hex. Until the start of the <style="Faction_Orks">Rukkatrukk</style>'s next turn, the first time a marked hex is occupied by an enemy, that enemy takes <style="Stat_Hits">{[nrOfHits]}x</style> <style="DMG_Blast">{[minDmg]}-{[maxDmg]} Blast Damage</style>, and the mark is removed. When a friendly unit occupies an affected hex, it does not take damage, and the mark is removed.

Initial <style="Cooldown">cooldown: {[initialCooldownTurns]} round</style>. 

{[S/AbilityDamageExplanation]}

Targets a hex on the battlefield. Deals <style="Stat_Hits">{[nrOfHits]}x</style> <style="DMG_Flame">{[minDmg]}-{[maxDmg]} Flame Damage</style> to all enemies that are on <style="Effect_Fire">Fire</style> hexes or have taken <style="DMG_Psychic">Psychic Damage</style> this turn. Then adds <style="Effect_Fire">Fire</style> to the targeted hex.

Initial <style="Cooldown">cooldown: {[initialCooldownTurns]} round</style>. 

{[S/AbilityDamageExplanation]}
